ed Kingdom to enforce those three unterminated treaties over Hong Kong sovereignty ( the Treaty of Nanking; the Convention of Peking; the Second Convention of Peking ).<br />\n<br />\n(4) We demand Anglo-American or Nato joint military base in Hong Kong on a permanent basis, the expense of which will be covered by ourselves!<br />\n<br />\n(5) Hong Kong should and is going to be an independent Commonwealth nation.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ec494150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a>"},{"pid":"8f6f328cdbeae20bfb9dcb62344597dfb8e2f236","tid":1704094,"uid":124722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"收咗錢緊係笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd13b2809a600be710712a65b05c59f0fe2d33c","tid":1704094,"uid":203681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564b8c4f73d5e08a7a0821eb575c1c94cf2c19ca","tid":1704094,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf27b1767701e956e771c3ec2fa473810d3b23a","tid":1704094,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor